column4: <content>1 zw/w foto. With T. Harris in 1932 called 'C. Matsys', but figures different for tree see Brussels drawing dated 1541. Figures more like L. Gassel, Paysage avec scènes évangeliques (Brussels, exh. 1963, N° 101, Puyvelde, colourphoto 29. Christ fighting the wolf, cf. Pieter Stevens, Christ as the Good Shepherd. Graz, Joanneum, cat. 1923, N° 120, repr. in An Zwollo, 'Pieter Stevens' [Ein vergessener Maler des rudolfinischen Kreises], Jb.d.Kh. Slgn in Wien [= Jahrbuch der kunsthistorischen Sammlungen in Wien; Bd. 64, N.F. XXV], 1968, [pp. 119-180], fig. 164 (p. 121) and discussed p. 127. When the shepherd and his herd leave the stable, the thieves break in by the window.</content>
<documentation.title>Pieter Stevens, Ein vergessener Maler des rudolfinischen Kreises</documentation.title>
